p.01703376c4a81c0e9d91: Activates workflow exclusively when app runs in sc.runtime, otherwise remains inactive.
p.01703376c4a81c0e9d92: This component serves as a gatekeeper in your application's workflow, ensuring that a specific process is only initiated when the app is running in the designated sc.runtime environment. If the app is not in this environment, the process remains inactive, providing precise control over when the flow is triggered.
